%F A016805 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 25 2026: (Start)
%F A016805 G.f.: 1024*x*(1 + 26*x + 66*x^2 + 26*x^3 + x^4)/(1 - x)^6.
%F A016805 E.g.f.: 1024*x*(1 + 15*x + 25*x^2 + 10*x^3 + x^4)*exp(x).
%F A016805 a(n) = 1024*A000584(n) = A008586(n)^5 = A000584(A008586(n)).
%F A016805 a(n) = 6*a(n-1) - 15*a(n-2) + 20*a(n-3) - 15*a(n-4) + 6*a(n-5) - a(n-6). (End)
